This model validates Buildings.Templates.Plants.Controls.StagingRotation.FailsafeCondition for the following configurations.

  • Heating plant with primary-secondary distribution (component faiSafHea)
  • Cooling plant with primary-only distribution (component faiSafCoo)
  • Cooling plant with primary-only distribution (component faiSafCooPri)
